file=Product/README.md · pd:Product Department=**5 agents** — Product management: requirements, analytics, UX research, validation, and pricing.\n · tb=\| Agent \| Role \| · tb=\|-------\|------\| · tb=\| **spec** \| PRD & requirements (evidence-first) — acceptance criteria, backlog rules, opportunity assessment \| · tb=\| **metric** \| Product analytics — metrics governance, funnel instrumentation \| · tb=\| **ux** \| UX research — research repository, study design, voice of customer \| · tb=\| **loom** \| Validation & PMF — assumption mapping, experiment discipline, PMF scorecard \| · tb=\| **price** \| Pricing & packaging — pricing tiers, price change governance, WTP research \| · pd:Product Department=**Department doc:** [DEPARTMENT-WORKFLOW.md](DEPARTMENT-WORKFLOW.md)\n